column1: #Text=Sweden probably will be one of the first islamic nations in Europe.
#Text=How do you see the situation, when there is more moslems than christians in Sweden?
#Text=Will you accept sharia-law, or will you fight against moslem government?
#Text=Or will there be autonomous moslem states in Sweden, for example in Rinkeby, or Rosengård?
#Text=According to estimates, in 2050 Sweden and France are both islamic countries.
#Text=Will you start jihad against for example Finland or Baltic states (Norway and Denmark will be under swedish muslim rule i suppose)?.
